room_title: Escape room "Observation" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description:
You and your friends decided you wanted a little extra cash to pay bills. So you all signed up to be a part of a psychological trial. All you are supposed to do is play some games while they watch you from a camera. Simple right?
But why do they ask you to take a pill first? That wasn’t supposed to be part of the deal. Maybe something more sinister is happening. You might want to find out what is really going on and find out what was in that pill. Who knows what it will do to you…
